cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC 

The paper discusses guidelines for designing domain specific languages, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. It also mentions existing guidelines for general purpose languages (cs.PL), modeling languages (cs.LG), and the importance of user acceptance (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of DSLs in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
